365
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:56,660
You can trust Zhao's judgment.

366
00:32:57,420 --> 00:32:58,340
I know.

367
00:33:00,940 --> 00:33:01,900
Jiawen is totally

368
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:03,340
bad at cooking.

369
00:33:03,900 --> 00:33:05,660
