The speech hasn't started yet.

447
00:39:14,620 --> 00:39:16,180
Grandma, where's Yangao?

448
00:39:16,180 --> 00:39:17,470
Inside. Go on.

449
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,420
There's food and drinks.

450
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:19,260
Mom.

451
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:20,460
Go on.

452
00:39:21,980 --> 00:39:24,300
